data.description: Location, location, location known as ''The Island'' of Mansion Hill. Family owned since 1960.  Possible 4 bedroom being sold ''AS-IS'' in this prime location.  Close proximity to Interstates 471, 75/71 and 275 to downtown  Cincinnati, Ohio. Minutes to downtown Cincinnati. Central Air Lennox HVAC system.  Pine flooring, Rookwood FP, are a few notable features of the property.  Close to Dora District in Bellevue, KY and Newport on the Levee. Many notable venues, businesses, store fronts within minutes. Parcel site on a double lot, 136 & 137.  Full fenced in yard with paver brick lined pathway.  Schools are Newport city schools, not county.  Newport Elementary, Newport Intermediate, Newport High.
